        What Your Real Estate Agent Does During Your Sale Campaign
      </h1>
      <p style="font-size:1rem;color:rgba(240,236,228,0.6);line-height:1.8;max-width:54ch;">
        A straightforward breakdown of what your agent should be doing from listing to settlement, and how to tell if they are actually doing it.
      </p>
